title: Hellhammer Apocalyptic Raids A.D. 1990
description:
Hellhammer was an influential early 1980s extreme metal band from Switzerland. They are regarded as a key influence on black metal, and frontman Thomas Gabriel Fischer stated they "would later be credited as being among the founders of death metal." Two ex-members went on to form the equally important Celtic Frost in 1984

This torrent contains the following albums
